         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">1/10/90 ¶  ¶ It was a pleasant surprise to me, dear Miss Rolleston, to receive with your kind inscription the volume on the "History of Ballarat", ¶  a place visited by me, when it was a small lot of ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">90.10.01a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Mary Rolleston</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Archives, Miscellaneous correspondence. </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter found in Kew Museum Library's copy of B88.12.01 and transferred to RBG Kew Archives. The book is inscribed 'To Miss M. F. Rolleston for friendly acceptance and occasional use from the writer of these pages. Sept. 1890'. A calling-card printed with M's coat of arms and 'Baron Ferd. von <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mueller. K.C.M.G. M.&amp; Ph.D. F.R.S.' is pasted below the dedication.</p>
               </note>1/10/90</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It was a pleasant surprise to me, dear Miss Rolleston, to receive with your kind inscription the volume on the "History of Ballarat",<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">The book has not been positively identified. The most likely candidate is Withers (1887).</p>
               </note> a place visited by me, when it was a small lot of tents only. By this thoughtful gift of yours I am also reminded of my generous friend, Mr Oddie,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Probably James Oddie (1824 -1911); but could be his brother Thomas Ralph Oddie (1830-1927).</p>
               </note> so that I have sent him also a private copy of the "Select plants" to Ballarat.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With regardful remembrance your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">There are two associated envelopes:</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.6681in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; "
                     xml:lang="en">(a) In M's hand:</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.5516in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">Miss Mary Rolleston</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.5516in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">82 Nicholson- Street</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.5516in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">Fitzroy</hi>
                     </seg>.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.6681in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; "
                     xml:lang="en">[Annotated in another hand, in the top right corner above the address: </p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.6681in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; "
                     xml:lang="en">'Oct 1890. Baron von Muller | Melbourne']</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.6681in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; "
                     xml:lang="en">(b) in an unknown hand:</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.5516in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">Sir Ferdinand Müller</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.5516in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">[or] Baron Ferd. von Müller</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.5516in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">Arnold St.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.5516in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">St Kilda Road</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 9pt; margin-left: 0.5516in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                     xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
